{"word":"H7164 - קָרַס - qâraç - kaw-ras' - Stoop","slug":"H7164","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָרַס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâraç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-ras'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Stoop"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05E1; - qa&#x0302;ras</b> - <i>kaw-ras'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>protrude</i>; used only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H7165\">H7165</a> (for alliteration with <a href=\"#/H7167\">H7167</a>), to hunch, that is, be humpbacked: - stoop."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7026\">H7026</a>, <a href=\"#/H7165\">H7165</a>, <a href=\"#/H7166\">H7166</a>"}]}